#### About 

This is a shop that I made in WordPress that uses Woo-Commerce. On it I sell clothing and art work. All of the designs and art work are created by me. 

#### Development

The site is just a simple WordPress - Woo-Commence online shop. I wanted something simple and reliable. 

The store does use drop shipping so I did have to integrate Printful's API intro Woo-Commence but luckily they made that easy. 

In the future I may re-build the site with Shopify which I can easily integrate into a Next.Js site. 

##### Full List Of Technology Used

- WordPress
  - Used to create and manage the site.
- Woo Commerce
  - Used for the e-commence.
- Printful
  - Used to for drop-shipping of the products. 
- Site Ground
  - I host the site on Site Ground. It is one of a few sites I have. 

#### Design

The design of my store follows the design of my clothing. It is colorful, vibrant, and yet minimal. 

